i watched #ParasiteMovie yesterday and came away uneasy. the underlying theme seems to be that rich people are innocent victims of their own success and the poor are conniving rascals who will exploit that success. i can’t approve of that message.

FYI- I am really not good at pitching movies that I like to other people. If I say it's good, that's hella something. I also like seeing movies where you can't describe the plot without giving away the magic. With all that said - #ParasiteMovie was *fantastic*
